{
    "name": "Troglodyte Tyrant",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Troglodyte tyrants come from the enlightened troglodytes who live far deeper underground than common troglodytes. Stronger, more intelligent, and longer-lived than their degenerate kin, they find it easy to assert dominance over tribes of normal troglodytes. Warlike in the extreme, tyrants are seasoned veterans of numerous military campaigns and they are expert tacticians, willing to sacrifice large numbers of troglodyte warriors to probe an enemy\u2019s strengths and weaknesses."
        }
    ],
