                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": " The tyrant casts <i>amplify stench</i> on herself and <i>bull\u2019s strength</i> on a trusted ally. She then uses her <i>wand of bear\u2019s endurance</i>."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": " When combat begins, the tyrant casts <i>rage</i> on her allies\u2014though she doesn\u2019t concentrate on it. She then casts <i>divine power</i> on herself if the enemies haven\u2019t reached her yet. She casts <i>mark of the reptile god</i> and <i>bestow curse</i> on strong enemies, then fights in melee."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Base Statistics",
                "text": " Without <i>amplify stench</i> and <i>bear\u2019s endurance</i>, the tyrant\u2019s statistics are <b>Aura </b>stench (30 ft., DC 19, 10 rounds); <b>hp </b>113; <b>Fort </b>+15; <b>Con </b>18."
